      <title>美光因台湾地震导致 DRAM 供应受到影响</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/micron-flags-hit-its-dram-supply-taiwan-earthquake-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[内存芯片制造商美光科技 (Micron Technology) 周四表示，4 月 3 日发生在台湾的地震将使其动态随机存取内存 (DRAM) 供应量损失高达中个位数百分比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/micron-flags-hit-its-dram-supply-taiwan-earthquake-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦洪水致逾98,000人疏散</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/over-98000-people-evacuated-due-floods-kazakhstan-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦紧急情况部周四表示，由于洪水，哈萨克斯坦已有超过 98,000 人被疏散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/over-98000-people-evacuated-due-floods-kazakhstan-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:20:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与越南房地产公司相关的顶级资产被指控数十亿美元的欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/top-assets-linked-vietnam-property-firm-accused-multibillion-dollar-fraud-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南有史以来最大的金融诈骗案的主谋、万盛发控股集团董事长张美兰在经过一个月的审判后于周四被判处死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/top-assets-linked-vietnam-property-firm-accused-multibillion-dollar-fraud-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:10:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>评级下调和政府调查后万科股价、债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-vanke-shares-bonds-fall-after-rating-cut-government-probe-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在标准普尔取消其投资级地位以及该开发商证实一名高管正在接受调查的报道后，万科的股价和美元债券周四下跌，加剧了陷入困境的房地产行业的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-vanke-shares-bonds-fall-after-rating-cut-government-probe-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯从远东航天发射场发射首枚安加拉-A5太空火箭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-launches-angara-a5-space-rocket-vostochny-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯周四在远东东方航天发射场首次试射安加拉-A5太空火箭，成功将测试负载送入低轨道，作为开发后苏联时代新型运载火箭的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-launches-angara-a5-space-rocket-vostochny-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在菲律宾-日本峰会上对北京在南海的举动发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-warn-beijings-south-china-sea-moves-philippines-japan-summit-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国、日本和菲律宾领导人齐聚白宫，反击北京在有争议的南海问题上对马尼拉加大施压，周四，中国与其邻国之间长期存在的紧张关系将成为人们关注的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-warn-beijings-south-china-sea-moves-philippines-japan-summit-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:09:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南大亨因125亿美元诈骗案被判处死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-tycoon-sentenced-death-12-billion-fraud-case-state-media-reports-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体报道，越南一家法院周四对房地产大亨张美兰 (Truong My Lan) 判处死刑，罪名是她参与了该国有记录以来规模最大的 304 万亿盾（125 亿美元）金融欺诈案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-tycoon-sentenced-death-12-billion-fraud-case-state-media-reports-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举失败后，妥协可能会更好地服务好斗的韩国总统</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-election-rout-compromise-may-better-serve-south-koreas-combative-president-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通过不妥协、有时甚至是好斗的政治上台后，韩国总统尹锡烈如果希望在选举惨败后保护自己的遗产和政党，他可能不得不重新考虑他的标志性风格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-election-rout-compromise-may-better-serve-south-koreas-combative-president-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:57:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>解释者：日本为何寻求与拥有核武器的朝鲜举行峰会？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/why-is-japan-seeking-summit-with-nuclear-armed-north-korea-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登周三表示，他支持日本总统岸田文雄尝试与朝鲜领导人金正恩进行面对面会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/why-is-japan-seeking-summit-with-nuclear-armed-north-korea-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:53:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国大选将如何重塑尹的政策议程</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-south-korea-election-may-reshape-yoons-policy-agenda-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在其政党在立法选举中惨败后承诺续任，其结果增加了他的更多政策重点可能偏离轨道的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-south-korea-election-may-reshape-yoons-policy-agenda-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 06:20:48 GMT</pubDate>
